Changelog

Source: NEWS.md

rstanemax 0.1.3 (in development) Unreleased

Minor changes

rstanemax 0.1.2 Unreleased

Minor changes

  • You can now fix Emax with emax.fix argument for stan_emax() function.

rstanemax 0.1.1 2019-11-19

Breaking changes

  • For posterior prediction, the column name of the newdata needs to be the same as the one in the original input data, instead of exposure in the previous version.

Major changes

  • stan_emax() can now incorporate categorical covariates in select parameters. See vignette("emaxmodel") for detail.

rstanemax 0.1.0 2019-05-31

Initial CRAN release
